    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just... i feel like i'm already dead, you know? like i'm just a ghost haunting this house. everyone says \"it gets better\" or \"time heals,\" but they don't get it. they aren't living in this void. sometimes i sit here and i think, if the most important part of my life is gone, then what's left? it feels like i'm just dragging this heavy, meaningless body around for no reason at all. it feels more like a burden than a life.",
